Privacy Policy:
Information Collected:
We, Lays Game Studio, may collect certain types of information when you use our mobile applications ("Apps"):
Personal Information: We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and any other information you provide when you contact us.
Automatically Collected Information: Our Apps may automatically collect certain information, including device information (e.g., device type, operating system), usage information (e.g., app features used, time spent in the app), and other analytical data.
Use of Information:
We use the collected information for the following purposes:
App Functionality: To provide and enhance the functionality of our Apps.
Communication: To respond to your inquiries and provide support.
Analytics: To analyze usage patterns and improve our Apps.
Third-Party Services:
Our Apps do not utilize any third-party services that collect user data.
User Consent:
By using our Apps, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Security:
We implement reasonable security measures to protect the confidentiality and integrity of the collected information.
Data Retention:
We retain collected information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
User Rights:
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. Please contact us at
laysgamestudio@gmail.com
for assistance.
Privacy Policy Updates:
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our data practices. Updates will be effective upon posting, and we will notify users of any significant changes.
Contact Information:
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at
laysgamestudio@gmail.com
.
By using our services, you indicate your agreement with this Privacy Policy.
